<P>
   &UR; WRESTLING (Available by 2 p.m., Wed., Sept. 22):
</P>
<P>
   ALI vs. INOKI: Watching a pay-per-view event wasn't always as
easy as it is today. You needed more than a remote control. Not so
long ago, events were broadcast on ``closed-circuit TV'' and shown
in sporting venues. Such was the case with the ballyhooed
