   Y2K-CORPS _ ATLANTA _ The power grid is secure, the telephone
lines ready. Every big company from Georgia Power to BellSouth has
developed a Y2K contingency plan and tested and retested it. So
what could go wrong? Plenty _ only no one knows for sure what.Such
is the state of corporate Atlanta as it awaits with baited breath
the turn of the century. (Haddad, Atlanta Journal-Constitution).
25.
</P>
