<P>
   _ ``Candid Camera,'' the show created by Cornell graduate
 &UR; Allen Funt &LR; , who died earlier this month, is used in that
university's basic psychology courses.
</P>
<P>
   Psychology 101 students see an episode wherein an elevator
passenger is joined by three others who turn to face one side of a
car. Most of the time Passenger A turns to face the same way as the
rest, unable to resist the pressures of conformity.
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
