   &UR; WHO SAID WHAT &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ``I wouldn't call it work. If you exercise your index finger,
it's not terribly exacting. You know ... there goes another one! I
never thought of it as a career. I was very busy trying to avoid
anything that might entail illustration of my feelings.''
</P>
