addition, other state institutions are seen as remote and
unresponsive.
</P>
<P>
   He said the country's two main political parties are seen as
having set up a spoils system that has led to the squandering of
the country's vast oil wealth.
</P>
<P>
   In fact, despite having the largest oil reserves outside the
Middle East, nearly 80 percent of the Venezuelan population lives
